headline: Tom's of Maine Introduces Whiten+ Toothpaste to Canada: Natural, Effective, Whitening
summary: Tom's of Maine, a certified B Corp and leader in natural and effective personal care, proudly announces the launch of Tom's of Maine Whiten+ Toothpaste in Canada. This innovative whitening solution combines naturally derived micro-polishers and plant-powered cleansers to remove 95% of surface stains in just two weeks with twice-daily brushing.
